Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:06.87,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:15.30,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:27.60,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.19,0:00:40.76,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Creation Magic: Leo Rugiens!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:53.00,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you've got,\NCaptain of the Crimson Lion Kings?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:04.71,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,In the instant you attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:08.31,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,for just a moment, the barrier's \Nmana thins in places.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.64,0:01:10.52,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I aimed for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.91,0:01:13.94,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.61,0:01:16.44,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Rades, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.76,0:01:20.91,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you possess extraordinary abilities \Nand polish them to their fullest,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:25.41,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,without a righteous spirit,\Nyour deeds are nothing but violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.01,0:01:29.29,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,No one will acknowledge something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.31,0:01:36.09,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I need to get stronger so things like \Nthis don't give me so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:38.75,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early for you to \Nbe cheering just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.13,0:01:43.22,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I think everything's just about ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.92,0:01:46.72,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Now for some lively sow's mana...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.72,0:01:49.36,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,How exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.01,0:02:09.87,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I would always close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.87,0:02:14.21,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And cower at reality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.21,0:02:18.88,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:23.26,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Of just making excuses to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:24.40,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand right there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.40,0:02:25.54,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be near you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:26.68,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Any minute now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:30.06,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait right there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:30.06,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(The decisive battle is still a long way off)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:32.15,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Black and blue
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:38.07,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give up on giving up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.07,0:02:41.57,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And get the world on my side
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.57,0:02:45.23,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for the reason I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:50.46,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time somewhere under this sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:56.32,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Break through the tearful nights
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:59.59,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And head where the light shines
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.59,0:03:03.43,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to keep my promise
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:06.97,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deliver it to you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:10.96,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,shape of love
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:18.69,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Blackout
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:24.57,italics,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.52,0:03:29.45,italics,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I have magic that's stronger\Nthan anyone else's.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:35.12,italics,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I studied everything there was about my \Nmagic, polished my skills, and prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:38.46,italics,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,All for this day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:41.01,italics,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,For years... and years!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:48.28,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,And yet... Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:10.20,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle, I thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:12.58,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You can save the thanks! Just hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.93,0:04:14.33,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,But of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.23,0:04:24.08,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Magic: Ignis Columna!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:47.36,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you like that?! I made him \Nevaporate with intense firepower!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:50.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:52.39,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent! Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:55.08,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,You are definitely a man worthy\Nof leading this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:56.58,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:04:59.08,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I accidentally saluted, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.91,0:05:04.38,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.69,0:05:10.95,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! I've got as much magic as a royal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:11.85,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:15.85,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Flame-Binding Magic: Leo Palma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:24.56,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.56,0:05:26.12,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:28.36,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:31.87,top,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.11,0:05:31.87,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,There are many questions I'd like to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.51,0:05:37.37,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,But before that, I will be \Nconfiscating your grimoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:39.58,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:45.16,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch my grimoire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:49.09,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,What is this grimoire?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:50.72,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:57.48,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one page?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:06:00.88,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! Don't look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:04.91,italics,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,He can only use one spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:03.31,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:07.09,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:10.32,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare look down on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:12.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna look down on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:24.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you think of any other way to get \Npeople to acknowledge your power?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:34.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You have amazing magic, and you were\Nstrong enough to claw your way up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:35.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.84,0:06:44.27,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Here. I'll lend you my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:46.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:50.78,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,What you lacked to overcome adversity...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:54.03,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,was a righteous heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:56.79,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Pay for your crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:59.79,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Are you satisfied now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:02.42,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,A voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:04.13,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:10.27,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,It was impossible for you to beat \Na captain on your own after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:12.05,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:12.88,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:18.85,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,The sheer volume of your magic isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:21.67,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also reaching my limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:23.79,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,You're through acting on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:27.71,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, things are \Ngoing to go as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:29.57,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,All for our master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:32.07,sign_10872_95_West_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,West District
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:35.84,main,Guy 1,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Knights are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.84,0:07:38.12,main,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray for the Golden Dawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:42.12,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, I think I'll go have some dessert.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:44.40,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to join me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.89,0:07:47.04,main,Shiren,0000,0000,0000,,I will decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.04,0:07:49.57,sign_10872_95_West_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,541)}East District
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.31,0:07:51.67,main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:56.31,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back to our lodgings and \Nwash off all this sweat, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.31,0:07:57.35,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:08:00.14,main,Guy A,0000,0000,0000,,Great job, Blue Rose Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:03.25,main,Lady 1,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Charlotte is so elegant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:05.43,main,Lady 2,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Charlotte is so lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:07.06,main,Lady 3,0000,0000,0000,,Sol is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:12.82,sign_10872_95_West_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Central District
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:21.04,italics,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,What is their motive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:24.06,sign_10872_95_West_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,539)}Northwest District
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:36.63,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they're in the marked areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:45.73,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,My grimoire...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:49.06,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:54.95,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:58.75,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,No—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:00.62,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.79,0:09:18.59,main,People,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.84,main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Knights...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:27.35,main,Lady 2,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Charlotte... disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:29.35,main,Lady 3,0000,0000,0000,,Sol...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.95,0:09:49.97,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:52.29,main,Shiren,0000,0000,0000,,It would appear that we're at least
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:55.25,main,Shiren,0000,0000,0000,,a few hundred kilometers \Naway from the royal capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.25,0:09:58.84,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,They got us! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.40,0:10:01.96,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,They managed to infiltrate the royal capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:07.77,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I figured they must've had a rather \Nskilled spatial magic user, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:10.19,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,To think they were able \Nto send us all this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.61,0:10:13.92,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Curses!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.37,0:10:16.65,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:19.13,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Knights' mana...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:21.11,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,I can't feel it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.04,0:10:27.62,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,This is unprecedented spatial magic. \NWas there another spellcaster?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:33.39,main,Man C,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.39,0:10:35.38,main,Lady A,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:49.90,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,To think the great Magic Knights would \Nall fall for a silly trap like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:51.64,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid can they be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:57.32,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I was supposed to play with the stragglers, \Nbut it looks like I won't have to bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:11:02.66,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... I'd better use this \Ntime to get some nice, young mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:07.48,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Ash Curse Magic: Ash Absorbing Formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:14.46,main,Man E,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:17.25,main,Lady C,0000,0000,0000,,No! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:24.52,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent. Just look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:26.74,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,My skin is silky smooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:28.76,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Even water would bounce right off of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:33.52,main,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,No! Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:37.90,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Stop acting all cute, you sow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:49.24,main,Hot guy,0000,0000,0000,,Eliza! W-Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:54.54,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Well, aren't you a handsome young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:12:01.73,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think I'm pretty?\NHow old do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.73,0:12:02.76,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:06.43,main,Hot guy,0000,0000,0000,,H-How could you? You monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.97,0:12:09.40,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a monster?! Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:18.98,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:22.90,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I guess someone was able to \Nescape that spatial magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.65,0:12:36.75,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,My, you're hot {\i1}and{\i0} my type.\NSay, want to have some fun with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:39.40,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from those people,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:41.00,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,you old hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:44.97,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I'll murder you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:13:03.82,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,My, you're hot {\i1}and{\i0} my type.\NSay, want to have some fun with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:06.43,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from those people,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:08.07,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,you old hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:11.24,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I'll murder you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.19,0:13:14.24,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling an old hag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.93,0:13:17.63,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Ash Curse Magic: Cheerful Ash Destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:23.50,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,These are curse bullets \Nwith various curses inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:31.43,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,You won't know what you'll \Nget until they hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:39.19,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you people? What are you after?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:42.61,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,My, my. Look at you, \Nwith such ample time to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:46.19,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since you're hot, \NI guess I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:50.61,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to eliminate someone.\NThat's our goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:52.24,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.24,0:13:54.99,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think it is, darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:01.13,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm definitely not going to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.33,0:14:08.41,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,You're working with at least one other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:12.01,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,A spatial magic user must have \Ninfiltrated the royal capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:14.51,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.68,0:14:18.27,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Have they already fled?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:22.89,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where you might've sent \Nthe rest of the Magic Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:26.53,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,you don't have enough power \Nto take over the royal capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:31.03,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine that this was \Njust to go after the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:35.53,sign_10872_95_West_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,King's Quarters
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:45.11,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,You've made it clear that \Nyour motive is revenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:48.01,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,but what are you and the \Nothers after overall?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:59.05,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Our true motive...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:03.06,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,is you, Fuegoleon Vermillion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:04.52,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:07.82,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Fuegoleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.37,0:15:09.57,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,What do you—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.07,0:15:15.03,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,This is spatial magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:18.83,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Nothing ventured, nothing gained.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:23.53,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Fuegoleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:30.83,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:16:02.56,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,The attacks keep coming. She has\Na tremendous amount of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:06.21,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,These ash bullets themselves \Ndon't do much damage, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:10.19,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:14.74,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right? It looks like you're \Nhaving a hard time getting around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:17.14,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what you've been hit with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:19.01,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.14,0:16:23.59,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I... can barely see anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:28.15,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gradually losing sensation\Nthroughout my body, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:32.11,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you hear me? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:38.16,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,My ears are also going... This is her power?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:44.04,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,My Ash Curse Magic: Cheerful Ash \NDestruction works very gradually.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:47.60,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,First, your eyes stop \Nworking, then your ears,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:49.52,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,and then your body stops moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:56.05,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay for having the \Ninsolence to call me an old hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:16:59.63,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,People expected a lot\Nfrom my four-leaf clover...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:04.60,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I even joined the top Magic \NKnights squad, the Golden Dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:10.02,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yet... what am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:14.64,flashback,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about a four-leaf clover?\NThat stupid peasant, getting a big head...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.64,0:17:19.39,flashback,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. He lacks the talent worthy to \Nbe a member of the Golden Dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:22.03,flashback,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he won't last long.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:24.79,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,All those voices around me don't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:30.54,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only bettering myself so I won't lose. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:32.71,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:37.86,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,What defeated that guy was \Na power I just happened upon,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:41.26,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,one that I can't control.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:43.72,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.69,0:17:47.89,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,That power doesn't seem \Nto want to listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:53.40,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,The only reason I was able to \Navoid the spatial magic earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:58.24,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,was because something other\Nthan my own power reacted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:03.20,flashback,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we're expecting \Nanything from that peasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:05.44,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:08.25,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,That's not why I'm frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:16.09,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you attacking?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:19.67,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,You have to aim properly, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:27.72,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,If you say, "I'm sorry, miss," and adorably \Nbeg for your life, I'll forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:30.27,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not a... chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:34.17,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see... anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:40.32,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I can't feel... anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:19:00.84,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,This is... the flow of mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.33,0:19:06.20,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It's said that mages with wind-based \Nmana are excellent at detecting mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:07.37,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,With all five senses cut off
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:10.35,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and his back against the wall,\NYuno's finely honed concentration
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.35,0:19:12.71,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,demonstrated an astonishing\Nability to detect mana,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:16.31,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and was attempting to go beyond even that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:23.75,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry up and beg for your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:26.13,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, I'm just \Ngoing to have to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.84,0:19:32.16,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many things I want \Nto ask you. Hey, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.16,0:19:34.71,main,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on. Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:37.73,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Would you shut up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.29,0:19:40.39,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't care less about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:43.22,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.09,0:19:47.18,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,don't want to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.51,0:19:50.47,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,to Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.98,0:19:53.31,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:20:02.99,italics,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,That grimoire... \NThe legendary four-leaf clover?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:17.50,italics,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Mana is gathering...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:20.75,italics,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,This sensation... He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.09,0:20:25.18,italics,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,He's controlling the mana?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.31,0:20:31.24,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I see. The spirit has constantly \Nbeen sending me mana signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:36.27,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I was relying so much on my sight and \Nhearing that I wasn't noticing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:42.03,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Let me just tell you one thing about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:44.71,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.71,0:20:47.03,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,hate losing more than anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:51.54,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Wind Spirit Magic: Sylph's Breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:55.29,italics,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,No! I have to use the magic \NI stole to defend myself, or I'll—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.43,0:21:15.55,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.37,0:21:42.74,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,My dry emotions gaze at the me from that day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.74,0:21:45.71,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And push me forward
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.71,0:21:47.75,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I can't find a place to go)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.75,0:21:53.03,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the faintest light can \Nstill break through the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.03,0:21:58.53,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And change the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.27,0:22:00.95,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I will keep believing in you)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.95,0:22:03.83,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In this ever-vivid place
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.83,0:22:06.78,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Break free yourself)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.78,0:22:09.67,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to grasp my endless dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.67,0:22:12.33,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is a path that I should choose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:14.39,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Do you wanna try? Do you wanna try?)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.39,0:22:17.30,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever it may lead us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.30,0:22:19.79,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Until my life comes to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.79,0:22:22.47,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will accept any pain that comes my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.47,0:22:24.49,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(We can try again, we can try again)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.49,0:22:28.85,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we can't see tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.85,0:22:34.40,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding onto feelings too intense to voice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.97,0:22:38.13,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep screaming them in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.03,0:22:53.49,sign_33083_276_Petit_Clover_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,520)}Pe{\c&H3BC020&}t{\c&HE2AF0F&}i{\c&H3BC020&}t C{\c&HE2AF0F&}l{\c&H3BC020&}o{\c&H0E42D4&}ve{\c&H3BC020&}r
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.19,0:22:52.89,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:56.99,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(521,1)}Birthday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.21,0:22:55.28,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.75,0:23:00.25,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to get the wind \Nspirit to listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.25,0:23:03.76,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I shall name her Bell,\Nand today is Bell's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.95,0:23:06.66,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,This cake is for you, Bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.66,0:23:07.80,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.80,0:23:10.25,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Should we say you're one year old?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.01,0:23:13.76,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday, Bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:15.51,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,So pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.91,0:23:18.72,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Make a wish and blow out the candles.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.72,0:23:20.31,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.21,0:23:31.83,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's the cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.83,0:23:33.25,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.67,0:23:38.08,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! What did \Nyou do with my brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.08,0:23:39.58,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Answer wisely, or you shall face my wrath!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.58,0:23:43.12,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Fuegoleon! You... Fuegoleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.12,0:23:46.67,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 25: "Adversity."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.54,0:23:51.14,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 25\N\N{\fs18}Adversity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.67,0:23:47.96,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,I'm calm at all times...
